Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.31,0:00:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无限的时间将跳动停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们悄声无息地燃烧着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.03,0:00:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何人注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界已经脱轨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被红世之火所包围
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紫你也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.51,0:02:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是火焰之雾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使命是与红世之徒战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界真正的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.40,0:02:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.03,0:02:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.49,0:02:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要修复这城市的歪曲看来需要你帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,8)}{\bord2\1c&H3535FF&\3c&HCFCFCF&}在战斗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丘莉小姐所说的密斯提司
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.48,0:03:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悼词咏唱者的助手是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 田中也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这应该是我说的话才对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然是密斯提司
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的坂井悠二呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井悠二…已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.76,0:03:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…意外的很坚强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般不会用这种口气说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.22,0:03:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是担心被大家知道了该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算刚才也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 必须去找吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.59,0:03:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的事被她知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后受了很大的打击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以得赶快解释
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.43,0:03:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算解释也没什么意义了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实终归是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多米诺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魂之圣庙差不多到了完成阶段了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 教授
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像火焰之雾们完全不明白那到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…看来那个的目的并不是扩大歪曲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.57,0:04:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会出现歪曲也许是其他计划的副作用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…因为「探耽求究」是个喜欢做无用功的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微去看下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:05:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 到底想让我做这种无聊的事到何时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启作和荣太还没到玻璃檀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍旧没有那痴呆教授的气息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明派出那么多磷子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来还有另一个火焰之雾在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道和探耽求究有没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接去问不是更快些么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去问问吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这些磷子的力量不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是火焰之雾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.23,0:05:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丘莉说过又进来了一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个…是这个的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:05:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个让吉田同学看到了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了…我也必须快点去玻璃檀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是…火炬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紫是火焰之雾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…在这城市所发生的事情和坂井同学的事全都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都知道了却还…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却还喜欢坂井同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经能一个人跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…原来是悼词咏唱者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才在战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得感到一股子粗暴的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊…这不是老爷子们嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能松口气了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎和神经病教授没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你们也对感觉不到探耽求究的气息抱有疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底设置了什么机关
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是密斯提司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不是  没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来怎么一副死样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…这么说来你就是坂井悠二吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…没想到居然是密斯提司
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了对不起那小姑娘的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么把她卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很适合作我们的协助者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适合？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这种随便的理由就把这个给她了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道突然看到了那些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会受到多么大的打击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学明明什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一定要拖她来我们的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.99,0:08:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.49,0:08:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎对你来说是相当重要的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学是个温柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个不可以来我们世界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该一直待在原来的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经身处无法回来的地方了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…把你卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然画面不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但首先得看清现实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…对对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于那个自在式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.15,0:09:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对它的实体稍微有些眉目了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:10:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和吉田一美那种人没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也不像夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会说那种话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个自在式的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是利用城市的歪曲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在空间里挖洞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空间里挖洞？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬把拼板的其中一块拆下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话就容易理解了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既明白又不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做这种事到底有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…探耽求究从很早以前就经常做莫名其妙的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 确实对城市有着影响
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以马上开始调律才是上策
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像昨天和你说明的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能协助我们进行调律吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说协助？继续将吉田同学卷进来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放着不管的话 城市会变得更加乱七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:10:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和卡姆辛先生约定好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且已经不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很对不起刚才逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.96,0:11:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.93,0:11:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「卡迪修的心室」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂~~~什么也没发生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好像稍微有点问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…因为那个自在式的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.83,0:11:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在城市里标下的印记不能动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说不能进行调律了的意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐 听得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 因为发生了很多事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦 玻璃檀启动了没？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.43,0:12:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在城市上空的自在式某处有个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市中到处弥漫了的自在式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中到了一处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.54,0:12:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在河上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.06,0:12:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概在祭典主会场附近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说自在式的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在祭典主会场的河边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是塔台那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都感觉不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来探耽求究把大部分是机器做成的磷子当作助手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「助人为乐」多米诺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…本该想到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那东西的话感觉不到气息也很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:12:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打倒那个磷子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自在式也能破解了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着这个 联络用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 丸子西亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会说："一起去吧"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魂之圣庙前言的数字控制在预计范围之内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来所接受委托的实验就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出~~~色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.97,0:13:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来就准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我所带来样品自在式进行预备实验吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…火焰之雾接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那里就自己想办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先前往集中点了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信结束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 别突然动手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.55,0:14:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这玩意是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布有歪曲存在之力的防御自在式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼呼呼…你们的攻击是无效的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始变形
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…有什么意义么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天晓得…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 刚才的机关确实挺麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危险了无法出手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.83,0:14:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神经病教授
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在城市外面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…看来没打算躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:14:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得感觉不到气息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.28,0:15:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…但准备从哪里进来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很明显地在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好~~~要上咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞艇？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探耽求究做事总是毫无意义的夸张
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这个作战本身毫无意义也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特意从空中来是有意义的也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.27,0:15:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才说过那里的空间有一块拼板被拆掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那飞艇也许是最后的拼板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小男孩的说法也有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那机器人 去扰乱那空间不是更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正飞艇也有同样的机关啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.73,0:16:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算攻击也没效的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 万一真是这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造出那空间的自在法也会受到影响的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要接近那空间的话 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要解开自在式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…还有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么意外的话我会一起行动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话真想拒绝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.21,0:16:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不到悠二的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二…好远
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  变形完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.15,0:17:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 火焰之雾们放马过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.73,0:17:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是高潮&华丽的最后一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.88,0:17:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自在法解除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往Van Berry的街角
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘着马儿去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.02,0:17:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管到哪都有伴奏 嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰之雾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子在发神经呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你再随心所欲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妨碍我探究神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这帮思考停滞的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多米诺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.08,0:17:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让他们瞧瞧珍藏已久的必杀技
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又变得奇怪了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对只是想这么做而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这简直可以称为「双保险」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请避开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽快击落它的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？要动手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷子要发飙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快离开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  不战斗就大胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合不合体根本没什么意义嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有意义是由我来决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是来干啥的…那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.89,0:19:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.43,0:19:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学…是这么温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经治不好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…真正的我已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.73,0:20:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类？我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为身体和心都是这么的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…人类
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢这样的坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.38,0:20:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.82,0:20:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…发动「卡迪修的心室」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.12,0:21:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 请想象你城市的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据这个来纠正歪曲  进行调律
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.83,0:21:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从出生以来一直居住的这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.14,0:21:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个温暖的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.63,0:21:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.88,0:21:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二他…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.44,0:21:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二他不会和我一起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.78,0:22:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.88,0:22:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比鲁海尔米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说有些做得过分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.25,0:22:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探耽求究
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.31,0:22:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的工作可是事先准备而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.23,0:22:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验本身已经成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.07,0:22:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可没资格发牢骚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实  一定会顺利进行的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回预告
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.74,0:24:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与怀念的比鲁海尔米娜重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.34,0:24:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她却敏感地察觉到了夏娜的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.56,0:24:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后她逼着夏娜做出了一个决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.68,0:24:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 无情的比鲁海尔米娜
